I was invited here as a guest.

298
00:24:43,273 --> 00:24:45,817
I won't just drink
whatever you tell me to drink.

299
00:24:45,901 --> 00:24:47,152
I'm not that dumb.

300
00:24:47,652 --> 00:24:49,029
Where do you think you are?

301
